1
00:00:06,801 --> 00:00:07,719
Ah..

2
00:00:08,011 --> 00:00:09,763
Am I crazy?

3
00:00:19,064 --> 00:00:20,857
Did you get home safe?

4
00:00:21,691 --> 00:00:22,984
Yeah

5
00:00:24,861 --> 00:00:26,947
I have a can of beer left

6
00:00:28,281 --> 00:00:29,366
Drink it

7
00:00:31,159 --> 00:00:32,494
Alone?

8
00:00:34,621 --> 00:00:37,624
Bring it tomorrow if you don't wanna drink alone

9
00:00:44,923 --> 00:00:46,967
To where?

10
00:00:52,681 --> 00:00:54,474
Let's talk tomorrow

11
00:00:56,059 --> 00:00:57,268
Okay

12
00:01:11,366 --> 00:01:13,368
Heard your blind date asked you out again?

13
00:01:13,368 --> 00:01:14,369
Did you reply?

14
00:01:15,453 --> 00:01:16,079
I did

15
00:01:16,705 --> 00:01:17,831
Really? What did you say?

16
00:01:18,665 --> 00:01:20,375
Told him to find someone good

17
00:01:21,292 --> 00:01:22,210
Hey!

18
00:01:22,210 --> 00:01:23,461
What?

19
00:01:24,254 --> 00:01:26,673
I told you to see him a few more times

20
00:01:27,173 --> 00:01:28,466
I'm tired

21
00:01:30,301 --> 00:01:30,969
Hey

22
00:01:31,511 --> 00:01:34,973
Your standards are way too high

23
00:01:37,684 --> 00:01:38,560
Hey

24
00:01:38,893 --> 00:01:40,353
But hey..

25
00:01:40,895 --> 00:01:42,313
Are you seeing someone lately?

26
00:01:44,524 --> 00:01:45,900
I'm not

27
00:01:47,986 --> 00:01:49,696
I don't think so?

28
00:01:50,113 --> 00:01:51,031
Lately, looking at your phone

29
00:01:51,031 --> 00:01:52,490
You keep smirking

30
00:01:52,824 --> 00:01:54,993
Never getting annoyed even when working OT

31
00:01:56,953 --> 00:01:59,164
Stop talking nonsense

32
00:02:01,583 --> 00:02:03,293
It's fucking suspicious

33
00:02:13,678 --> 00:02:15,013
Welcome

34
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:19,893
Is Jieun not working today?

35
00:02:19,893 --> 00:02:21,227
Ah, Jieun?

36
00:02:21,227 --> 00:02:22,437
She has the day off today

37
00:02:23,104 --> 00:02:24,314
Ah..

38
00:02:26,066 --> 00:02:26,566
Okay

39
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:43,416
[Text message 30 mins ago]

40
00:02:45,251 --> 00:02:47,253
It's my day off today

41
00:02:47,921 --> 00:02:49,881
Can I bring the beer over?

42
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:54,177
Just saw the message

43
00:02:54,886 --> 00:02:56,179
Where are you?

44
00:02:58,223 --> 00:02:59,641
At home

45
00:03:01,059 --> 00:03:02,477
Come out

46
00:03:08,483 --> 00:03:10,193
To where?

47
00:03:14,364 --> 00:03:15,657
In front of the convenience store

48
00:03:17,367 --> 00:03:19,077
It's cold out there

49
00:03:20,787 --> 00:03:22,914
Then where is better?

50
00:03:28,878 --> 00:03:31,464
Wanna come to my place?

51
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:56,322
What are you doing not coming in?

52
00:03:57,448 --> 00:03:59,075
How did you know?

53
00:04:01,369 --> 00:04:03,872
I could hear all the rustling

54
00:04:04,664 --> 00:04:05,832
Ah..

55
00:04:26,769 --> 00:04:28,271
You play guitar?

56
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,858
No, I don't

57
00:04:33,651 --> 00:04:35,069
Then why?

58
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,655
Wanted to learn

59
00:04:37,655 --> 00:04:39,365
I just stuck it on the wall

60
00:04:51,336 --> 00:04:53,254
Your hair used to be short

61
00:04:55,215 --> 00:04:56,674
In my freshman year

62
00:04:57,592 --> 00:04:59,427
I had short hair back then

63
00:05:03,139 --> 00:05:04,766
It looks better now

64
00:05:06,434 --> 00:05:07,685
Thank you

65
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:19,781
But why did you take a gap year?

66
00:05:21,783 --> 00:05:24,827
School was a bit hard

67
00:05:26,037 --> 00:05:26,996
Like what?

68
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,750
The people

69
00:05:33,211 --> 00:05:34,504
Ah..

70
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,881
Ah, like getting bullied?

71
00:05:37,966 --> 00:05:39,759
Not like that

72
00:05:40,301 --> 00:05:42,136
Just..

73
00:05:42,136 --> 00:05:45,598
I often felt I was a bit different

74
00:05:46,933 --> 00:05:48,935
Different how?

75
00:06:04,659 --> 00:06:07,078
But honestly, me too

76
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:13,876
Others go to gatherings

77
00:06:13,876 --> 00:06:15,545
Go on blind dates

78
00:06:15,545 --> 00:06:18,506
Date and break up with boyfriends

79
00:06:20,049 --> 00:06:21,843
I don't envy that

80
00:06:24,345 --> 00:06:26,389
Even if I go on blind dates

81
00:06:27,473 --> 00:06:30,393
Whether I like the person or not

82
00:06:31,019 --> 00:06:33,771
I don't really get the feeling itself

83
00:06:38,901 --> 00:06:40,695
But

84
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,408
But?

85
00:06:47,744 --> 00:06:50,455
Lately I kind of get it

86
00:06:51,873 --> 00:06:53,082
Get what?

87
00:06:55,335 --> 00:06:59,005
What missing someone feels like

88
00:07:05,303 --> 00:07:07,388
Missing someone..

89
00:07:07,388 --> 00:07:08,181
Is it me?

90
00:07:10,266 --> 00:07:11,601
Unnie, are you okay?

91
00:07:11,601 --> 00:07:12,310
Yeah

92
00:07:12,477 --> 00:07:13,394
I'm fine

93
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,688
Ah, and it's not you

94
00:07:15,688 --> 00:07:17,440
So don't say weird things

95
00:07:21,194 --> 00:07:21,944
Okay

96
00:07:23,946 --> 00:07:24,822
Ah..

97
00:07:25,323 --> 00:07:27,367
It's a bit hot

98
00:07:27,909 --> 00:07:29,619
Should I open the window?

99
00:07:29,952 --> 00:07:30,787
No..

100
00:07:31,621 --> 00:07:32,663
No, it's fine

101
00:07:49,931 --> 00:07:51,391
Are you sleepy?

102
00:07:53,518 --> 00:07:56,562
No, I'm not

103
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:01,109
You are dozing off right now

104
00:08:03,694 --> 00:08:05,780
Just because of working OT

105
00:08:07,407 --> 00:08:08,991
You can sleep

106
00:08:11,369 --> 00:08:12,787
I won't sleep

107
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,880
Unnie?

108
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:21,272
Did I fall asleep?

109
00:09:21,814 --> 00:09:22,899
A little

110
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:26,819
I'm sorry

111
00:09:28,613 --> 00:09:29,697
Unnie

112
00:09:34,202 --> 00:09:37,163
What you said earlier about missing someone..

113
00:09:38,372 --> 00:09:40,541
Was it really not me?

114
00:09:45,546 --> 00:09:49,842
You asked if there's anything good at the store

115
00:09:49,842 --> 00:09:52,929
You didn't answer that

116
00:09:55,431 --> 00:09:56,974
That's

117
00:09:58,768 --> 00:10:00,353
Still..

118
00:10:01,103 --> 00:10:02,605
Don't you know?

119
00:10:25,253 --> 00:10:27,880
What is this?

120
00:10:29,006 --> 00:10:30,633
A kiss

121
00:10:33,219 --> 00:10:35,263
I know that but..

122
00:10:36,556 --> 00:10:38,182
Did you hate it?
